### About me
I'm a software developer at the University of Washington. I work on [opendatakit](http://opendatakit.org/).

### My side projects

[Language](https://github.com/nathanathan/Language) - A crowdsourcing approach to natural language programming.

[cfg-gen](http://nathanathan.github.com/cfg-gen/) - A Interface for generating things from context-free grammars.
